===Usage notes===
*Unlike Mandarin, '''tang-sai''' does not mean ''something'' or ''thing'' in Min Nan.  Use [[mi虓h-ki膩鈦縷mi{{unicode|虓}}h-ki膩鈦縘] instead.  For ''thing'' in the abstract sense, use [[t膩i-ch矛]].